thumb.title: [MMD] Nyaonix, 歌手音ピコ, 鏡音レン - Dream Fighter
thumb.description: I hope you all enjoy this little blast of the past with this cover and mmd video!! I had so much fun rendering my first mmd video!! Perfume is my favorite jpop group so it was a lot of fun to cover them again! I love how the Nyaonix Lat model turned out sooo much!! Thank you so much NyxQuentiam for all your help! Download NYAONIX LAT here! https://www.mediafire.com/file/h3yjnf9r5kjgsdj/LAT+NYAONIX.zip/file 〖Vocal(s)〗Nyaonix Append, Kagamine Len Append v2, Utatane Piko v2 〖UST〗プディンセス 〖Model(s)〗LAT, NyxQuentiam, VenusSempai, Megumi777 〖Stage(s)〗youkan 〖Motion(s)〗わさび, RituPepper (Ri2Pepper) 〖Effects〗Diffusion 7, Light Bloom, Power DOF, Autoluminous, Trackdancer for the mics!
